tswitem.name: Impenetrable Augment Resonator
tswitem.tooltip:
Impenetrable Augment Resonator
An unattuned healing augment.
Resonating this augment to an active ability will increase the power of barrier effects by 1%/ 2%/ 3%/ 4%/ 5% for this ability.
To attune this augment, place it in the assembly window with:
  • 2 Attuned Mending Augment Resonators
  • 60 Pure dust
